track.description:
DJ Sotofett takes over #GCWradio.

How can you not like that? We were pretty stoked about it. That DJ stalker Jimmy Winkles earned his crust on this one. (I think he is currently lurking in the bins outside Fred P's studio)

Turns out that Sir Sotofett is an avid listener of us stumbling around the turntables. Good, because I have been hammering his mixes also. It's a massive love in. Vibes.

He hasn't got a Soundcloud that I can find so i'm putting it up.
